#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:13
msgid "Contribute to Weblate"
msgstr "Cur le Weblate"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:20
msgid "Weblate is developed by an open community."
msgstr "Tá Weblate forbartha ag pobal oscailte."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:21
msgid ""
"There are many ways you can contribute to Weblate development. Talk about it "
"with your associates."
msgstr ""
"Tá go leor bealaí inar féidir leat cur le forbairt Weblate. Labhair faoi le "
"do chomhpháirtithe."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:25
#: weblate_web/templates/download.html:24
msgid "View sources"
msgstr "Féach ar an gcód foinseach"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:27
msgid "Translate the app"
msgstr "Aistrigh an aip"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:34
msgid "Found a <strong>bug</strong> in Weblate?"
msgstr "Ar aimsigh tú <strong>fabht</strong> i Weblate?"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:38
#, python-format
msgid ""
"In case it is sensitive or a <strong>security issue</strong>, please report "
"it to %(report)s. Other ways of reporting security issue can be found in the "
"<a href=\"%(url)s\">documentation</a>."
msgstr ""
"Má <strong>fadhb slándála</strong> nó fadhb íogair atá ann, déan tuairisc ag "
"%(report)s. Is féidir amharc ar bhealaí eile le tuairisc a dhéanamh sa <a "
"href=\"%(url)s\">cháipéisíocht</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:41
#, python-format
msgid ""
"<strong>Ensure the bug is not already reported</strong>, by searching "
"through the <a href=\"%(url)s\">GitHub issues</a>."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Déan cinnte nár tuairiscíodh an fabht cheana féin</strong>, trí "
"chuardach a dhéanamh trí na <a href=\"%(url)s\">fadhbanna ar GitHub</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:44
#, python-format
msgid ""
"If you're unable to find an open issue addressing the problem, <a "
"href=\"%(url)s\">open a new one</a>."
msgstr ""
"Muna féidir leat fadhb oscailte a aimsiú a bhaineann le d'fhadhb, <a "
"href=\"%(url)s\">oscail ceann nua</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:47
#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:77
msgid ""
"<strong>Follow instructions in the issue template</strong>, and provide as "
"much relevant info as possible."
msgstr ""
"<strong>Lean na treoracha i dteimpléad na faidhbe</strong>, agus cuir "
"isteach an t-eolas ar fad atá agat."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:50
#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:80
msgid "GitHub issues"
msgstr "Fadhbanna GitHub"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:54
msgid "Have a <strong>patch</strong> that fixes a bug?"
msgstr "An bhfuil <strong>paiste</strong> agat a dheisíonn fabht éigin?"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:58
#, python-format
msgid "Open a new <a href=\"%(url)s\">GitHub pull request</a> with the patch."
msgstr ""
"Oscail <a href=\"%(url)s\">iarratas tarraingt GitHub</a> nua leis an bpaiste."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:61
msgid ""
"Ensure the pull request description clearly describes the problem and "
"solution. Include the relevant issue number if applicable."
msgstr ""
"Cinntigh go bhfuil cur síos soiléir sa chur síos ar an iarratas tarraingte "
"ar an bhfadhb agus ar an réiteach. Cuir an uimhir eisiúna ábhartha san "
"áireamh más infheidhme."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:64
msgid "Open a pull request"
msgstr "Oscail iarratas tarraingt"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:70
msgid "Missing a <strong>feature</strong> or want to change something?"
msgstr ""
"An bhfuil <strong>Gné</strong> ar iarraidh duit nó an mian leat rud a athrú?"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:74
#, python-format
msgid "Suggest your change in the <a href=\"%(url)s\">GitHub issues</a>."
msgstr "Mol an t-athrú i <a href=\"%(url)s\">bhfadhbanna GitHub</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:84
msgid "<strong>Source code</strong> related questions?"
msgstr "Ceisteanna ag baint leis an <strong>gcód foinse</strong>?"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:88
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Please consult the <a href=\"%(url)s\">contributor documentation</a> to find "
"the most common topics."
msgstr ""
"Amharc ar <a href=\"%(url)s\">cháipéisíocht na ndeontóirí</a> chun na "
"hábhair is comónta a aimsiú."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:91
#, python-format
msgid ""
"Share what is on your mind in the <a href=\"%(url)s\">GitHub discussions</a>."
msgstr "Roinn do smaointí ar na <a href=\"%(url)s\">cainteanna GitHub</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:95
#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:114
msgid "Browse documentation"
msgstr "Brabhsáil cáipéisíocht"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:101
msgid "Want to help out with <strong>Documentation</strong>?"
msgstr "An bhfuil tú ag iarraidh cabhair le <strong>cáipéisíocht</strong>?"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:105
#, python-format
msgid ""
"The documentation is part of the main source code repository and you can "
"easily follow the links to edit each page directly from the <a "
"href=\"%(url)s\">documentation</a>."
msgstr ""
"Is cuid de stór na gcód foinseach an doiciméadú agus is féidir leat na naisc "
"a leanúint go héasca chun gach leathanach a chur in eagar go díreach ón <a "
"href=\"%(url)s\">doiciméadú</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:108
msgid ""
"Once you have a patch ready, please follow <a href=\"#patch\">patch "
"submission</a> instructions."
msgstr ""
"Nuair atá paiste réidh, lean treoireacha <a href=\"#patch\">aighneacht an "
"phaiste</a>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:111
msgid ""
"Help fix and suggest non-code related pull-requests by joining the reviewer "
"team."
msgstr ""
"Cabhraigh le hiarrataí tarraingthe nach mbaineann le cód a shocrú agus a "
"mholadh trí dhul isteach san fhoireann athbhreithnitheoirí."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:118
msgid "<strong>Financial support</strong> is always put to good use."
msgstr "Baintear dea-úsáid i gcónaí as <strong>tacaíocht airgeadais</strong>."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:120
msgid "Please open the donation page for options on how to donate."
msgstr ""
"Oscail an leathanach deonaithe le haghaidh roghanna maidir le conas síntiús "
"a thabhairt."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:121
#: weblate_web/templates/user.html:152
msgid "Donate now"
msgstr "Déan síntiús anois"

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:127
msgid "<strong>Are you a translator?</strong> Help translate Weblate itself."
msgstr "<strong>An aistritheoir thú?</strong> Cabhraigh le Weblate a aistriú."

#: weblate_web/templates/contribute.html:130
msgid ""
"You can translate Weblate and many other projects at <a href=\"https://"
"hosted.weblate.org/engage/weblate/\">hosted.weblate.org</a>."
msgstr ""
"Is féidir leat Weblate agus tionscadail eile a aistriú ag <a href=\"https://"
"hosted.weblate.org/engage/weblate/\">hosted.weblate.org</a>."

